data.title: Roy Acuff marker - Maynardsville, TN
data.meta_description: Country Music Hall of Famer Roy Acuff grew up in the town of Maynardsville, TN.  The Union County History Museum in town also has many Acuff display pieces.  This plaque (as well as one for Carl Smith) is located on a wall in front of the Union County Courthouse.
